OpenVPN Cookbook Chapter 12 sample code

The samples in this chapter are all openvpn configuration files, 
some server configuration files and some client configuration files.

Chapter 12 is divided up into 7 recipes. Below is a list of which
configuration file is used in which recipe.

12.1 Inline certificates
server: basic-udp-server.conf
client: example12-1-client.conf

12.2 Connection blocks
server1: basic-udp-server.conf
server2: example9-7-server.conf
client:  example12-2-client.conf

12.3 Port sharing with an HTTPS server
server: example12-3-server.conf
client: example12-3.ovpn

12.4 Routing features: redirect-private, allow-pull-fqdn
server: example12-4-server.conf
client: example12-4.ovpn

12.5 Handing out public IPs 
server:  example12-5-server.conf
client:  basic-udp-client.ovpn
scripts: proxyarp-connect.sh, proxyarp-disconnect.sh

12.6 OCSP support
server: example12-6-server.conf
client: basic-udp-client.ovpn
script: example12-6-ocsp.sh

12.7 New for 2.2: the 'x509_user_name' parameter
server: example12-7-server.conf
client: example12-7.ovpn
script: example12-7-client-connect.sh

